00:17:57.610 --> 00:18:00.900
How do we create communication
around such a location

00:18:00.900 --> 00:18:03.800
to make it even more
compelling to go there,

00:18:03.800 --> 00:18:05.470
to push more content.

00:18:05.470 --> 00:18:08.240
This is what I see as a
shared infrastructure.

00:18:08.240 --> 00:18:12.080
It's not only just
for water, it's

00:18:12.080 --> 00:18:15.380
a new community center
that's hopefully

00:18:15.380 --> 00:18:17.034
going to be generated.

00:18:17.034 --> 00:18:18.700
SABORE OLE OYIE: I
really like your idea

00:18:18.700 --> 00:18:22.510
