more to the
ecosystem that you're

00:19:55.700 --> 00:19:57.310
taking out of the ecosystem.

00:19:57.310 --> 00:19:58.566
SABORE OLE OYIE: Correct.

00:19:58.566 --> 00:20:00.560
KAI WULFF: And that's
very encouraging

