00:20:16.740 --> 00:20:20.600
As much as I love people writing
applications for mobile phones,

00:20:20.600 --> 00:20:23.560
but it can't be--
in my opinion--

00:20:23.560 --> 00:20:25.930
the ultimate outcome that
everybody in the world

00:20:25.930 --> 00:20:28.240
only writes applications.

00:20:28.240 --> 00:20:30.380
So the application needs
to serve something.

00:20:30.380 --> 00:20:33.850
And I had a discussion
this morning with somebody

00:20:33.850 --> 00:20:37.340
about how he would invest
in your business case

00:20:37.340 --> 00:20:38.780
in rural Africa.

00:20:38.780 --> 00:20:44.320
Now, of course, I usually
