00:20:44.320 --> 00:20:49.130
I'm very confident that
within a five-kilometer radius

00:20:49.130 --> 00:20:52.950
you might have three different
cultures clashing together

00:20:52.950 --> 00:20:58.990
in Africa, but I was
asking and everything

00:20:58.990 --> 00:21:02.710
